<% content_for :title, "FAQ" %>

<main class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-5xl gap-5 px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <section class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-200/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 via-white to-amber-50 p-7 shadow-sm sm:p-9">
    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-700">FAQ</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-black leading-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700 sm:text-base">
      Quick answers before your first session at the private court near Mt. Pleasent, DC.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
    <div class="grid gap-3">
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-4" open>
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Is pickleball right for me?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">If you want a sport that builds fitness, coordination, and social confidence without a steep learning curve, pickleball is a great fit for most people.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">Am I too old to start?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">No. Sessions are tailored by age group and movement needs, and many players start later and progress quickly with proper pacing.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">What if it is my first time?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">That is completely fine. Your first session focuses on fundamentals, court orientation, and simple rally progressions so you can learn with confidence.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">What do I need to bring to a session?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Bring court shoes, water, athletic clothing, and a paddle if you have one. If not, a paddle can be provided for your first session.</p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <%= link_to "See pricing", pricing_path, class: "inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100" %>
      <%= link_to "Contact Monsoud", contact_path, class: "inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-emerald-700 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-emerald-800" %>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
